NGC 5315是一个位于[[圆规座|圆规座]]的[[行星状星云|行星状星云]]。视星等为9.8，包裹着一颗14.2等的恒星。位于[[圆规座α|圆规座α]]西南5.2度处。该星云的盘状特征要放大200倍才可见<ref name=bakich2010>{{cite book | first=Michael E. | last=Bakich | date=2010 | page=162 | title=1001 Celestial Wonders to See Before You Die: The Best Sky Objects for Star Gazers | series=Patrick Moore's Practical Astronomy Series | publisher=Springer | isbn=1-4419-1776-4 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qEhpS7d5ZdAC&pg=PA475&dq=NGC+5315&hl=en&sa=X&ei=o28OUf6eIuzOmAXp-4CwAg&ved=0CDcQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=NGC%205315&f=false | access-date=2017-04-02 | archive-date=2017-04-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402172956/https://books.google.com/books?id=qEhpS7d5ZdAC&pg=PA475&dq=NGC+5315&hl=en&sa=X&ei=o28OUf6eIuzOmAXp-4CwAg&ved=0CDcQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=NGC%205315&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。英国天文学家[[羅夫·科普蘭|羅夫·科普蘭]]于1883年发现了该天体。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://spider.seds.org/ngc/cid.html|title=NGC Online Cross Identifications|language=en|last=Frommert|first=Hartmut|website=spider.seds.org|access-date=2018-10-27|archive-date=2018-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181027101424/http://spider.seds.org/ngc/cid.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
